<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Wirich IV. von Treuchtlingen, Hofmeister [Burggraf Friedrichs VI. von Nürnberg]</head><p>Der Rat bittet um zügige Schlichtung des Streits zwischen Erkinger von Seinsheim und Jakob Topler, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_54" id="27r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_54_r1l1"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wẏrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Trewtlingen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l2">hofmeiſter etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_54_r1l3">Lıeber her wẏrich / Vns hat 
<del rend="strikethrough">fur </del> wılhelm von Sawnſheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l4"><expan>verſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vvıe Er nü newlıch bey euch geweſen ſeẏ vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l5">euch gebeten hab / als von <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Erkingers von Sawnſheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l6">ſeins vettern wegen / daʒ Jr euch der ſache <expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l7"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Erkinger / vnd Jacob Topler <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> Burger <expan>vntervvinde<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l8">vnd Jn tag beſcheiden wölt / alſo daʒ die ſache ende <expan>neme
<del rend="strikethrough"><ex>n</ex></del></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſull </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l9"> <expan>hıecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd ſant Mıchels tag 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſchierſt </del> / Alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l10">den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Burger Jacob Topler daran geweiſet / daʒ Er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l11">der ſache auch hinter euch <expan>gegange<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd der bey euch <expan>blıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ıſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l12">Alſo daʒ dıe <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogenlich</expan> <expan>hıecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l16">Mıchels tag 
<add><ab facs="#facs_54_line_1576667499066_2470">gencʒlıch </ab></add> ende vnd auſʒtrag neme / Darümb ſo bıten vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l17">euch <expan>fleiſſıklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von des <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Burgers wegen / daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l19">euch <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache 
<add><ab facs="#facs_54_r1l18">alſo </ab></add> <expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dem <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Erkinge<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l20">dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> cʒu entſcheiden <expan>vntervah<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l24">vnd Jn 
<add><ab facs="#facs_54_line_1576667516591_2488">bederſeit </ab></add> darümb täge beſcheidet 
<add><ab facs="#facs_54_r1l22">vnd das endet </ab></add> ſo Jr ſchıerſt mügt / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_54_r1l23">Als etc </ab></add> Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l25">
<add>vnd lat vns des</add> ewr <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / <expan>vvıd<ex>er</ex></expan> vviſſen <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ııj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Barth<ex>olomei</ex></expan> <expan>Ap<ex>oſto</ex>lı</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_54" id="27r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Wyrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Trewtlingen, hofmeister etc. </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her Wyrich, uns hat Wilhelm von Sawnsheim
                            <expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wie er nü newlich bey euch gewesen
                        sey und euch gebeten hab als von <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Erkingers von
                        Sawnsheim, seins vettern, wegen, daz ir euch der sache
                                <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Erkinger und Jacob Topler,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger,
                            <expan>unterwinde<ex>n</ex></expan> und in tag bescheiden wölt, also daz
                        die sache ende <expan>neme</expan>
<expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <app>
<note><q type="date">sant Michels tag</q>29.09.1414</note>
</app>. Also <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den
                            <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burger Jacob Topler daran geweiset, daz er
                        der sache auch hinter euch <expan>gegange<ex>n</ex></expan> und der bey euch
                                <expan>blib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist, also daz die
                                <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogenlich</expan>
<expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und dem
                            <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> sant Michels tag <add>genczlich</add>
                        ende und ausztrag neme. Darümb so biten wir euch
                                <expan>fleissiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von des
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers wegen, daz ir euch
                                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache <add>also</add>
<expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dem <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Erkinge<ex>r</ex>n</expan> und dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> czu entscheiden
                            <expan>untervah<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet und in <add>bederseit</add>
                        darümb täge bescheidet <add>und das endet</add>, so ir schierst mügt,
                            <add>als etc.</add>, das <expan>wölle<ex>n.</ex></expan>
<add>Und lat uns des</add> ewr <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> wissen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Barth<ex>olomei</ex></expan>
<expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
